            "type": "text",
            "text": "Brand Personality"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Funded First is the knowledgeable insider \u2014 the mentor who's been inside the banking system and knows all the shortcuts lenders won't tell you. Confident, trustworthy, and results-oriented. Speaks plainly, avoids jargon, and always leads with the outcome: you will get funded."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Voice & Tone"
          }
